Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:41.19,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}It's cold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.76,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I really keep these?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:49.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's probably some mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.69,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mukae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:57.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:01.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:03.78,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ricchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can't let myself get my hopes up.{\i0}{reword kill one of the my's}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've already been rejected once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.60,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the usual, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.43,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.54,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.46,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking beautiful as always, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.67,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.21,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.92,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Should I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.88,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You're in shock over the news that Yurika-senpai eloped?{shorten}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.43,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell him about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.97,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kawabuchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:47.89,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.76,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I don't think he's in the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:54.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't expect to hear anything like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How must he feel about it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:15.38,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's the one that won the Prefectural Governor's Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.53,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better take it down quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.17,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,You take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.23,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the school will display a painting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.07,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,by a student who's involved in a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.07,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,We were told to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And what's going to happen to it after you take it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.69,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This painting is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.36,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,What's she to you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.11,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Had eyes for her, did ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You can take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care what happens to that painting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Your stupidity must be contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:16.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how stupid are you gonna be for somebody else's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. What about the painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I already said my goodbye to it back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten a present from someone recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Like something that was knitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:49.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\i1}I knitted Sentaro a sweater and used the leftover yarn to make the mittens!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's cruel. I knew it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This! It's called Lily-yarn or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I got it from Sachiko yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:06.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But what am I supposed to do with this string?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you...? You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, these are really warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Dammit! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we'll be changing classes again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess third years are split up according to their grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:00.31,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so you probably won't be in the same class as Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, you're goin' for college entrance exams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to go to college too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:12.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about becoming an elementary school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So Rikko's gonna be a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.68,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:21.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko used to say she wanted to have a bakery or cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What? When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.64,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You were a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:29.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you wanted a shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:35.04,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, where do you want to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:40.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I... haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, never mind about college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I might not even make it to the third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! The next make-up exam's the showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Start with these basic problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you some flash cards in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not cut out for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if you fail this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll just quit school an' get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:15.98,Background Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about my family, I can't afford to repeat a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't let you flunk this test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired. I need a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You're in the middle of these questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to rest, it'll have to wait 'til you're done with these problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! My head's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.48,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Ni-Nii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:20.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You look really happy when you're surrounded by children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're going to have a big family of your own
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,with lots of kids around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.48,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Chikko wet herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:37.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wet herself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.96,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, Chikko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The bath's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:48.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,My ma will dry your pants, so relax for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an unusual setup for a bath...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of soap, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:03.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this Sen's family's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:23.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We share the bath with Sentaro's family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:33.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I wish I had given the mittens to you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:38.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost spring, so you won't need to use them for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since you knitted the mittens, Ricchan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to wear them all year 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:49.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Condensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Drops often fall in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro lets out a yelp once in a while himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:04.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ricchan, why did you give me those mittens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why me and not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:21.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... if you've liked him all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon! How about havin' dinner here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Your pants aren't dry yet anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, your hair's soakin' wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:45.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:03.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't mean to say that to Ricchan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:08.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't get it out of my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:13.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Ricchan probably still has feelings for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.87,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sen, how did the make-up exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:30.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.31,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta thank 'im proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.44,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't seen Prince Bon lately.{ole Bon..maybe?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday, \Nhe passed out in class with a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so he's restin' up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.44,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, Ritsuko didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"Someday My Prince Will Come", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:18.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko. Would you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it. Huge, ain't it—Bon's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Bon for me, for helpin' me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Go on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:42.64,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:49.36,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, one of your classmates has come to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ricchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:01.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is your fever down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.95,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.44,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.98,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Eat them if you're up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you go out of the way to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:22.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... No. I didn't buy these. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.89,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:30.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan. He came here with you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you two out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He should've come in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You two have been together since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:51.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could be a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:57.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me, he's strong, built,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:01.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,and so handsome, he even takes my breath away once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:05.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, you're better off with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:13.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're saying, so don't say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:28.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, don't you like me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,you just don't have any confidence, so you're trying to keep your distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, you told me to have confidence in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:44.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Those words have saved me a number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But if it looks like you don't have confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:51.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I'll lose mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:00.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What the heck am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:06.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I've wished for all this time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.07,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.01,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.39,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet something happened between those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:51.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, let me tell you how I feel about you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:59.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Ricchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:00.57,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.56,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Your relatives can hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:17.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not muscular and maybe I'm not as manly as I should be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:22.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but when it comes to my feelings for you, Ricchan, I'm second to none!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You might catch my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.07,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're burning up! And you're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.15,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:48.02,Background Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:01.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't made any more progress with Ricchan, and it's already summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I was that bold when I had a fever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong with me when my temperature is normal?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Touch what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:13.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:13.63,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.94,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,East High Newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"The Olympus Has Thrown Down the Gauntlet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:28.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"The Olympus is going to win at this year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru to Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are still some old-fashioned jazz musicians around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.56,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the era of rock n' roll."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,They were handing this out all over school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.56,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you can't take this sitting down, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You two are gonna perform in the festival, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.09,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We start with "Moanin'" to fire up the people that saw us last year
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:58.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,an' fake 'em out thinking we're gonna do the same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But then we move into some other songs that we want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinkin' the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's choose our next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, we'd better practice every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,'Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:12.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.28,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Nii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:19.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.40,Background Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.70,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I got surprising news!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.43,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Dad says he's comin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.87,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,This way, the whole family can live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:49.61,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I'm actually scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:54.61,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,See, our dad, who was working far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.61,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,is coming home tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, I'm one of those that ain't got a place in the house too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.35,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-nii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.97,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're back late, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's Bon doin' here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:25.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Unlike with Kota and the other little ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,you remember how scary Dad was when he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.64,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:37.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma told me that Dad worked really hard an' quit drinkin' over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.24,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You got nothin' to worry about, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:46.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now how about comin' inside, an' we can prepare together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:46.66,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:55.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for lookin' after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I'm worried about, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:10.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Dope! What are you lookin' so serious for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I am serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon. Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:18.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.43,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-chan, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:23.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to practice tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:34.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,After all, playin' with you is the most fun I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.72,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-chan, what are you writin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Nah, that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's not comin' out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well. Let's get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bon. I'm sorry for lying to you.{\i0}
